      • toLinearDistance

        LinearDistanceMeasure toLinearDistance(TimeMeasure dt)

        Produces a linear distance travelled given a dt. The output unit is the corresponding distance unit to this velocity unit

        The unit of the input dt does not matter, as it will be converted to this measure's time unit
